    • interpreterTask

      public abstract AbstractTaskPET interpreterTask​(org.jsoup.nodes.Element xmlline, org.jsoup.select.Elements xmllines, java.util.Set<org.jbpt.pm.DataNode> datanodes) throws org.json.JSONException
      Interpreter for the BPMN file. It returns the AbstractTaskPET associated to a task, extracted from the xmllines
      Parameters:
      xmlline - the line that has as tag the correspondent PETLabel
      xmllines - the lines describing the task
      datanodes - the set of datanodes extracted from the BPMN file
      Returns:
      the AbstractTaskPET extracted from the xmllines
      Throws:
      org.json.JSONException - if it cannot read the Json correctly
